items.title: A la mexicana
items.description: Scrambled with fresh pico de gallo, served with your choice of homemade refried beans or our refried beans or garden salad.

items.title: With ham or bacon
items.description: Your way - scrambled or fried - and a side of either refried beans or our refried beans or garden salad

items.title: With chorizo
items.description: Spiced just right. Comes with your choice of house refried beans or garden salad

items.title: With nopalitos
items.description: A timeless classic. Tasty Mexican pear cactus strips cooked until tender, with a side of our refried beans or garden salad.

items.title: Divorciados
items.description: Two eggs, now amicably separated: one bathed in red salsa, the other in green, both atop crisp tortillas, with refried beans or garden salad keeping the peace.

items.title: Sorpresa (surprise!)
items.description: A gem from Doña Diana Kennedy’s notebooks: a freshly pressed tortilla, stuffed with a whole blanquillo, with our refried beans or garden salad. Then gently fried and smothered in the salsa of your choice. Served as a pair, because one is never enough.

items.title: Rancheros extra Rancheros
items.description: Our crispy artisanal tostadas (fried corn tortillas) with refried beans on top, bathed in whichever of our salsas, and served with a mighty chile on the side.

items.title: Omeletes’n
items.description: Filled with melted cheese, with your choice of peppers, or mushrooms. Or, if you’d rather go lighter, have them with just eggwhites and a side of our garden salad.
